WEBVTT

NOTE
Hand-authored captions for Olivia's 27-second introduction.
Timings align with the natural phrasing of the spoken script.

1
00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.600
Hello. I'm Olivia.

2
00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:07.800
I've read charts by hand for fifteen years.

3
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:12.400
Ask me a question, and I'll answer
using your actual birth chart —

4
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:16.800
calculated in real time,
not drawn from a template.

5
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.400
If the chart has nothing specific to say,
I'll tell you.

6
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.400
Astrology isn't entertainment.

7
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.200
So — what would you like to know?
